  "text": "Preparation of Rat Tail Tendon Collagen. Type I collagen was prepared from rat tail tendons as described by [CITATION_1] by the modified procedure of [CITATION_2] . This preparation yields type I collagen, mostly in its native, not cross-linked, triple-helical form [CITATION_3] .",
